WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.626
Hello, young word explorer.

2
00:00:01.626 --> 00:00:04.470
Welcome to Unit 3, Ready, Steady, Go!.

3
00:00:04.470 --> 00:00:08.534
This unit has 23 vocabulary cards in 4 learning groups.

4
00:00:08.534 --> 00:00:11.379
Group 1 is Parts of the Body.

5
00:00:11.379 --> 00:00:15.849
Listen for words such as head, arm, hand, finger, tummy, toe.

6
00:00:15.849 --> 00:00:18.288
Group 2 is Movement Action Words.

7
00:00:18.288 --> 00:00:22.758
Listen for words such as wave, hop, jump, clap, wiggle, nod.

8
00:00:22.758 --> 00:00:25.196
Group 3 is Healthy and Strong.

9
00:00:25.196 --> 00:00:29.667
Listen for words such as exercise, healthy, strong, water, sleep, energy.

10
00:00:29.667 --> 00:00:32.511
Group 4 is Command Words (for Instructions).

11
00:00:32.511 --> 00:00:36.575
Listen for words such as touch, turn, stand, reach, flap.

12
00:00:36.575 --> 00:00:46.735
For each word, listen and repeat, read five sentences, notice the word type, practise spelling, write your own sentence, and ask the tutor for help.

13
00:00:46.735 --> 00:00:49.580
You are ready to begin Unit 3.
